        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Indian Tribal Government Coronavirus (COVID-19) Disaster Assistance Cost Share Relief Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases to 100% the federal share of certain disaster assistance provided to Indian tribal governments in connection with COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019).</p>]]></text>
